o-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yrm1665702560304.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yrm1665702560304.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yrm1665702560304.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yrm1665702560304\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__creocc_213085\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__topic_d70442e1_d70443e1_d70444e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yrm1665702560304_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__codeblock_nnz_m11_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">creocc  Entity,  OccurrenceNumber</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__section_w1663ab1b7b5_w1664ab1b7_w1665ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__p_d70448e1_d70449e1_d70450e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">creocc \"P_ORDER\", -1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__topic_d46217e1_d46218e1_d46219e1_d46220e1_d46221e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222034e76\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__3\">\n Name of an entity where an occurrence is to be created.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_d6263e1_d6264e1_d6265e1__entry__3\">\n A whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__section_qbj_z5z_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222034e145\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__1\">&lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__1\">&gt;=0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_76b3fc531d9bdc669cf1b00defa6a56c__entry__2\">Statement executed successfully.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The entity name provided is not a\n                        valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1203</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_RANGE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yrm1665702560304__table_dh5_1vz_xbc__entry__3\"> The occurrence number is out of range.\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__topic_d46232e1_d46233e1_d46234e1_d46235e1_d46236e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222034e291\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__topic_d46237e1_d46238e1_d46239e1_d46240e1_d46241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222034e300\"> Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__p_d70472e1_d70473e1_d70474e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span> statement creates an\n            empty occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> at the position indicated by\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__p_d70475e1_d70476e1_d70477e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var> is:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__li_d31841e1_d31842e1_d31843e1\">&lt; <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—occurrence is added (appended) after the last occurrence in the hitlist (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hits</span>+1).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__li_d31844e1_d31845e1_d31846e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—empty occurrence is created, using the current occurrence number. The new occurrence is inserted before the old active occurrence, so the effect is to increase all subsequent occurrence sequence numbers by 1.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__li_d31847e1_d31848e1_d31849e1\">From 1 to the current number of occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>, plus 1 (inclusive)—an empty occurrence is created at the indicated position.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__li_d31850e1_d31851e1_d31852e1\">Greater than the current number of occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> plus one—<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to -1 and no occurrence is created.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__p_d70478e1_d70479e1_d70480e1\">If the component contains only the default (empty) occurrence for an entity, the first use of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span> does not add an additional empty occurrence, while subsequent uses do. If the default occurrence contains either an initial value or a field assigned a value with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/init</span> switch, it is treated as an existing occurrence and a second occurrence is created.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__section_vts_m3b_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222034e366\">Example: Converting Text to Occurrences </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the use of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span>\n            statement to create empty occurrences of an entity. The data originated as a text dump\n            of a database of video tapes. The following ProcScript shows the conversion from the raw\n            (unformatted) text into more meaningful data:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"yrm1665702560304__pre_s2n_q3b_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\nretrieve \"VIDEO_DONE\" ; get video data (text)\nsetocc \"VIDEO_DATA\", 1 ; position at first occurrence\n$10 = 0 ; zero counter\nrepeat\n message/nobeep \"loop counter = %%$10\"\n creocc \"VIDEO_DONE\", -1 ; make an empty occurrence\n if ($status &lt; 0)\n break\n endif\n V_NUM.VIDEO_DONE = TAPE_NUM.VIDEO_DATA\n $1 = START ; load start time (text) into $1\n call TEXT_TO_TIME ; convert to time storage, --&gt; $2\n V_START = $2\n $1 = end ; do the same for end time\n call TEXT_TO_TIME\n V_END = $2\n V_TITLE_1.VIDEO_DONE = \"%%TITLE_1.VIDEO_DATA%%TITLE_1A.VIDEO_DATA\"\n V_TITLE_2.VIDEO_DONE = \"%%TITLE_2.VIDEO_DATA%%TITLE_2A.VIDEO_DATA\"\n $10 = $10 + 1\n setocc \"VIDEO_DATA\", ($curocc + 1)\n if ($status &lt; 0)\n break\n endif\nuntil ($10 = $hits)\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpg1665702560533.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>remocc</a><p>Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setocc</a><p>Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnc1665702576977.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entname</a><p>Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exa1665702598712.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgk1665702598390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qzx1665702660750.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger create</a><p>Trigger that handles a user’s request to add or insert a new occurrence of the entity in a Form.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7435775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7435775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "creocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity. Explain this code creocc Entity, OccurrenceNumber Copy Example: creocc \"P_ORDER\", -1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Name of an entity where an occurrence is to be created. OccurrenceNumber Number A whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=0 Statement executed successfully. Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following creocc Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. -1203 <UPROCERR_RANGE> The occurrence number is out of range. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The creocc statement creates an empty occurrence of Entity at the position indicated by OccurrenceNumber . If OccurrenceNumber is: < 0 —occurrence is added (appended) after the last occurrence in the hitlist ( $hits +1). 0 —empty occurrence is created, using the current occurrence number. The new occurrence is inserted before the old active occurrence, so the effect is to increase all subsequent occurrence sequence numbers by 1. From 1 to the current number of occurrences of Entity , plus 1 (inclusive)—an empty occurrence is created at the indicated position. Greater than the current number of occurrences of Entity plus one— $status is set to -1 and no occurrence is created. If the component contains only the default (empty) occurrence for an entity, the first use of creocc does not add an additional empty occurrence, while subsequent uses do. If the default occurrence contains either an initial value or a field assigned a value with the /init switch, it is treated as an existing occurrence and a second occurrence is created. Example: Converting Text to Occurrences The following example shows the use of the creocc statement to create empty occurrences of an entity. The data originated as a text dump of a database of video tapes. The following ProcScript shows the conversion from the raw (unformatted) text into more meaningful data: operation exec retrieve \"VIDEO_DONE\" ; get video data (text) setocc \"VIDEO_DATA\", 1 ; position at first occurrence $10 = 0 ; zero counter repeat message/nobeep \"loop counter = %%$10\" creocc \"VIDEO_DONE\", -1 ; make an empty occurrence if ($status < 0) break endif V_NUM.VIDEO_DONE = TAPE_NUM.VIDEO_DATA $1 = START ; load start time (text) into $1 call TEXT_TO_TIME ; convert to time storage, --> $2 V_START = $2 $1 = end ; do the same for end time call TEXT_TO_TIME V_END = $2 V_TITLE_1.VIDEO_DONE = \"%%TITLE_1.VIDEO_DATA%%TITLE_1A.VIDEO_DATA\" V_TITLE_2.VIDEO_DONE = \"%%TITLE_2.VIDEO_DATA%%TITLE_2A.VIDEO_DATA\" $10 = $10 + 1 setocc \"VIDEO_DATA\", ($curocc + 1) if ($status < 0) break endif until ($10 = $hits) edit end; exec Copy Related Links remocc Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store. setocc Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence. $entname Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. $curocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist. $hits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. trigger create Trigger that handles a user’s request to add or insert a new occurrence of the entity in a Form. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}